=== Spec Example 6.21. Local Tag Prefix
--- from: http://www.yaml.org/spec/1.2/spec.html#id2783499
--- tags: spec directive tag

--- in-yaml(<)
    %TAG !m! !my-
    --- # Bulb here
    !m!light fluorescent
    ...
    %TAG !m! !my-
    --- # Color here
    !m!light green

--- test-event
+STR
+DOC ---
=VAL <!my-light> :fluorescent
-DOC ...
+DOC ---
=VAL <!my-light> :green
-DOC
-STR
